# Tide Gateway - Tor Configuration for Transparent Proxy

User tor
DataDirectory /var/lib/tor

# Transparent proxy port (iptables redirects TCP here)
TransPort 0.0.0.0:9040

# DNS port (iptables redirects DNS here)
DNSPort 0.0.0.0:5353

# SOCKS5 (for testing/manual use)
SocksPort 0.0.0.0:9050

# Virtual network for Tor DNS
VirtualAddrNetworkIPv4 10.192.0.0/10
AutomapHostsOnResolve 1

# Logging
Log notice stdout

# Security
SafeLogging 1
AvoidDiskWrites 1
